DarkMouse::
She landed with a thump and on her tail. She got up muttering under 
her breath. She nodded to Galvatron and started scurrying over 
towards the maximal signal.  She stayed close to the ground and stuck 
to the rocks.  Finally, she made her way on a ledge, just a few 
meters away from the scene.  She saw a maximal with one gun and 
holding back two preds. Or what ever they were. She hadn'd seend bots 
like that before and wondered what they were. She transformed into 
bot mode, then drew her pistol with the stun charges and took 
aime. "Don't move" she whispered.  Then pulled the trigger.

slow her 
> down enough for us to grab her?"
